                    html: '<p>Which of the following reactions will yield benzaldehyde as a product?</p><p><img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/dc5872d4-2443-49b1-a984-1e40ce58a68d-ad6f732f-442c-426b-9a27-373866363a38-image.png"/></p>',
                    sol: '<img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/d08de57e-17b4-4a01-aa8d-d4eddaa50729-9726782.png" style="width: 400px; height: 447px;"/>',
