                    html: 'Match List - I with List - II.<br /><img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/z2v-1YJvIqyVfhNGsV4bMMr5BoShdjyLRbD0MiD-rjo.original.fullsize.png"/><br/>Choose the correct answer from the options given below :',
                    sol: '<img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/tON_a59caiSjXxepBxtTO0V3O4q55xXaFlrID0Q2RPU.original.fullsize.png"/><br/>',
