                    html: "Match List I with List II<br />\\(\\begin{array}{|l|l|l|l|}<br />\\hline &amp; \\text{List - I} &amp; &amp; \\text{List - II} \\\\<br />&amp; \\text{(Molecule/Species)} &amp; &amp; \\text{(Property/Shape)} \\\\<br />\\hline \\text { A. } &amp; \\mathrm{SO}_2 \\mathrm{Cl}_2 &amp; \\text { I. } &amp; \\text { Paramagnetic } \\\\<br />\\hline \\text { B. } &amp; \\mathrm{NO} &amp; \\text { II. } &amp; \\text { Diamagnetic } \\\\<br />\\hline \\text { C. } &amp; \\mathrm{NO}_2^{-} &amp; \\text {III. } &amp; \\text { Tetrahedral } \\\\<br />\\hline \\text { D. } &amp; \\mathrm{I}_3^{-} &amp; \\text {IV. } &amp; \\text { Linear } \\\\<br />\\hline<br />\\end{array}\\)<br />Choose the correct answer from the options given below:",
