                    html: "Match List - I with List - II.<br />\\(\\begin{array}{ll}<br />\\text{List - I} &amp; \\text{List - II} \\\\<br />\\text{Reaction} &amp; \\text{Type of redox reaction} \\\\<br />\\text{(A) } \\mathrm{TiCl}_4 &amp; \\text{(I) } \\mathrm{e}^2, \\mathrm{t}_2^0 \\\\<br />\\text{(B) } \\left[\\mathrm{FeO}_4\\right]^{2-} &amp; \\text{(II) } e^4, t_2^3 \\\\<br />\\text{(C) } \\left[\\mathrm{FeCl}_4\\right]^{-} &amp; \\text{(III) } e^0, t_2^0 \\\\<br />\\text{(D) } \\left[\\mathrm{CoCl}_4\\right]^{2-} &amp; \\text{(IV) } \\mathrm{e}^2, \\mathrm{t}_2^3<br />\\end{array}\\)<br />Choose the correct answer from the options given below :",
