                    id: "69302ea7f356ebdcf52bbb8a",
                    type: "singleCorrect",
                    html: '<p>Match List I with List II</p><table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 500px;"> <tbody> <tr> <td>\u00a0</td> <td>List I<br/>\t\t\tCoordination entity</td> <td>\u00a0</td> <td>List II<br/>\t\t\tWavelength of light absorbed in nm</td> </tr> <tr> <td>(a) </td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mfenced close="]" open="["><mrow><mi>CoCl</mi><msub><mfenced><msub><mi>NH</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mfenced><mn>5</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></math></td> <td>I.</td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>310</mn></math></td> </tr> <tr> <td>(b) </td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mfenced close="]" open="["><mrow><mi>Co</mi><msub><mfenced><msub><mi>NH</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mfenced><mn>6</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></math></td> <td>II.</td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>475</mn></math></td> </tr> <tr> <td>(c) </td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mfenced close="]" open="["><mrow><mi>Co</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>CN</mi><msub><mo>)</mo><mn>6</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo></mrow></msup></math></td> <td>III.</td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>535</mn></math></td> </tr> <tr> <td>(d) </td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mfenced close="]" open="["><mrow><mi>Cu</mi><msub><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi></mrow></mfenced><mn>4</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup></math></td> <td>IV.</td> <td><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>600</mn></math></td> </tr> </tbody></table><p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below :-</p>',
