                    html: "Match List - I with List - II.</p>\\(\\begin{array}{l|l} & \\begin{array}{l} \\text {List-I} \\\\ \\text {(Si-Compounds)} \\end{array} & & \\begin{array}{l} \\text {List-II} \\\\ \\text {(Si-Polymeric/} \\\\ \\text {Other Products)} \\end{array} \\\\ \\hline \\mathrm{A} & \\left(\\mathrm{CH}_3\\right)_4 \\mathrm{Si} & \\text {I} & \\text{Chain Silicone} \\\\ \\mathrm{B} & \\left(\\mathrm{CH}_3\\right) \\mathrm{Si}(\\mathrm{OH})_3 & \\text {II} & \\text{Dimeric Silicone} \\\\ \\mathrm{C} & \\left(\\mathrm{CH}_3\\right)_2 \\mathrm{Si}(\\mathrm{OH})_2 & \\text {III} & \\text{Silane} \\\\ \\mathrm{D} & \\left(\\mathrm{CH}_3\\right)_3 \\mathrm{Si}(\\mathrm{OH}) & \\text {IV} & \\text{2 D- Silicone} \\end{array}\\)<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below",
