                    html: 'The standard heat of formation <math><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><msub><mrow><mo>\u2206</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow></msub><msubsup><mrow><mi>H</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>298</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msubsup></mrow></mfenced></math> of ethane (in <math><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></mrow><mo>/</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow></mrow></math>), if the heat of combustion of ethane, hydrogen and graphite are <math><mo>-</mo><mn>1560</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>393.5</mn></math> and <math><mo>-</mo><mn>286\u00a0</mn><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></mrow><mo>/</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi></mrow></mrow></math> , respectively is ________',
