                    sol: '<p>UV <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>\u2192</mo></math>\u00a0For sterilization surgical instruments<br/>Microwaves <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>\u2192</mo></math>Communication (Radar system)<br/>Infrared <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>\u2192</mo></math> Green house effect<br/>X-rays <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>\u2192</mo></math>\u00a0Study crystal structure</p>',
