                    sol: '(A) Graph between Magnetic susceptibility and magnetising field is :<br><img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/w6v7neqFdR-CKY5QHXeMsuJNxzt_Ryb_-DT5Kf25Y6E.original.fullsize.png"/><br/>(B) magnetic field due to a current carrying wire for $\\mathrm{x} &lt; \\mathrm{a}$ :<br>$\\mathrm{B}=\\frac{\\mu_0 \\mathrm{ir}}{2 \\pi \\mathrm{a}^2}$<br><img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/DBbnMu1FS8YbdYjigrdXvHoiKf-CCbi5e4s2Je0eLcs.original.fullsize.png"/><br/>(C) magnetic field due to a current carrying wire for $x&gt;a$ :<br>$\\mathrm{B}=\\frac{\\mu_0 \\mathrm{i}}{2 \\pi \\mathrm{a}}$<br><img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/rxnQegHyDMRw8sORCOjfmJUPDJg3ujEHQBXAj9yeC1g.original.fullsize.png"/><br/>(D) magnetic field inside solenoid varies as:<img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/1IUO5wNN4u-DehvXVngWe4YIKVVikZ3G1MBjlrf-oCA.original.fullsize.png"/>',
