                    sol: '<p><img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/d5a336c8-c102-4e72-a6b4-3d57c2563933-image.png" style="width: 300px; height: 231px;"/></p><p>(1) Aniline is Lewis base give acid base reaction with <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>AlCl</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math> and form Anilinium ion<br/>(2) Anilinium ion has strongest deactivated ring so further Friedel Craft alkylation not occurs.</p>',
