                    html: "Which one among the following resonating structures is not correct?",
                    sol: '<p><img src="https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq_book_2024/81c9b9a8-13ec-43de-bb26-e0dde906ab1d-image.png" style="width: 212px; height: 102px;"/></p><p>It is unstable resonating structure\u00a0(due to similar charge on adjacent atom)</p>',
